<taxonomicName authorityName="Van Deusen" authorityYear="1969" box="[2221,2380,2839,2868]" class="Dothideomycetes" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Pteropus" kingdom="Fungi" order="Chiroptera" pageId="79" pageNumber="137" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="gilliardorum">gilliardorum</taxonomicName>
in accordance with Article 31 of the International Code of Zoological Nomenclature. Monotypic.
</subSubSection>
</paragraph>
